                  "text_1": "<strong>The Harsh Trusth</strong>",
                  "icon_1": "error",
                  "filled_icon_1": true,
                  "text_2": "The modern beauty industry has conditioned us to believe that \"more\" is better, but the reality is that the constant friction of brushes, the weight of thick pigments, and the frantic 7:00 AM rush are causing micro-stress to our skin that no amount of concealer can truly hide.",
