              "text_gTHFHb": {
                "type": "text",
                "settings": {
                  "visibility": "always-display",
                  "text": "<p>The problem isn't your skill level or the quality of your expensive palettes; it’s the physical toll of the \"application marathon.\" When we rush to blend stubborn pigments with dry brushes, we tug at the delicate dermis, inadvertently highlighting the very fine lines and texture we were trying to soften. We are trapped in a loop of over-consumption and physical skin fatigue.</p>",
