                "type": "text",
                "name": "Text",
                "settings": {
                  "visibility": "always-display",
                  "text": "<p>For years, the industry ignored the fact that our skin is a living organ, not a canvas to be painted. The Luminous Aura changes the narrative by using sonic technology—the same tech used in high-end facial cleansers—to \"tap\" pigment into the skin rather than rubbing it on top. This preserves the skin barrier while the pH-adaptive formula ensures you never look \"overdone.\" </p><p>It isn't just a makeup tool; it's a way to reclaim the health of your face while looking exactly like the best version of yourself.</p>",
