                  "content": "<p>The formula contains specialized molecules that react to the moisture and pH levels of your skin's surface. Within 30 seconds of application, the pigment shifts to create a custom rosy or coral hue that perfectly complements your specific skin undertone, ensuring you never look \"washed out\" or overdone.</p>",
