                  "content": "<p>Absolutely. In fact, it is safer than manual blending. Manual rubbing creates friction and heat, which can lead to broken capillaries and redness. The 12,000 micro-vibrations per minute act as a gentle \"stipple\" effect, depositing color without ever pulling or dragging the delicate dermis.</p>",
