                  "content": "<p>The Luminous Aura features a medical-grade, non-porous silicone head. Unlike traditional sponges that soak up bacteria and old product, you simply wipe the silicone tip with a damp cloth or a gentle cleanser. It dries instantly and is ready for your next application.</p>",
