                  "content": "<p>While the Luminous Aura is designed to be an all-in-one replacement for blush, lip, and eye tint, the sonic wand itself is a fantastic tool for blending your favorite liquid foundations or concealers. The vibration helps \"melt\" any external product into the skin for a more natural, airbrushed finish.</p>",
